column2: SELECT TOP # t.thingid, t.ndetect, d.objid, p.objid as besttObjid, p.psfMag_r, p.ra, p.dec, p.airmass_r FROM thingIndex AS t JOIN detectionindex AS d ON t.thingid = d.thingid JOIN Galaxy AS p ON d.objid = p.objid JOIN run r on p.run=r.run and p.rerun=r.rerun  WHERE t.ndetect > # AND p.ra between # and #  and p.dec between # and #
